<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konstanz und Ravensburg</head><p>Der Rat hat von einem Tag zu Konstanz mit Anwesenheit des Königs gehört und bittet um Mitteilung der Teilnehmer, der Themen und sonstiger Neuigkeiten.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_24" id="10v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_24_r1l12">Coſtäncʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_24_r1l13"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Vns iſt geſagt woꝛden / vvie daʒ ein tag beẏ ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l15">cʒu Coſtäncʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_24_line_1570706805792_36">werde </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſein ſulle / darcʒu vnſ </del> <expan>kürcʒlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan></del> ſulle </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l16">darcʒu ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der Römiſch künig / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vn </del> ſelber vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l17">auch ſüſt vil fürſten / <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vnd Ritterſchaft / kumen werden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l18"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr vns an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wiſſen laſſen wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l22">
<del rend="strikethrough">vvarumb ſie doſelbſt hın kumen <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> oder waʒ ew 
<add><ab facs="#facs_24_line_1570706991137_54">
<del rend="strikethrough">bey diſem <expan>bote<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab></add> vvaʒ ſie </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_24_r1l19">bey dıſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>bote<ex>n</ex></expan> vver als do hin <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> werde </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l26">
<add>vnd waʒ ſie</add> do cʒeſchicken mainen / oder waʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">gewerbe seyn werde dauon </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_24_r1l25">von den <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>newe<ex>n</ex></expan> leuffen </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_24_r1l27">
<add>bey ew</add> wiſſent / <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vveiſheit das füglich ſeẏ / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_24_r1l28">Rafenſpurg <expan>S<ex>imi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_24" id="10v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Costäncz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns ist gesagt worden, wie daz ein tag bey
                        ew czu Costäncz <add>werde</add>
<expan>kürczlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein sulle, darczu
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>,
                        der römisch künig, selber und auch süst vil fürsten,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und ritterschaft kumen werden.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir uns an
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wissen lassen wöllet <add>bey disem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bote<ex>n</ex></expan>, wer als do hin
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> werde</add>
<add>und waz sie</add> do czeschicken mainen oder waz ir <add>von den
                                    <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>newe<ex>n</ex></expan> leuffen</add>
<add>bey ew</add> wissent, <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit das füglich sey. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Rafenspurg <expan>s<ex>imi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
